ORG 100         / Start address of the program

INIT, LOAD 0    / Initialize counter (i) to 0
STORE I         / Store counter in I
LOOP, LOAD I    / Load the counter into the AC
SUBT THREE      / Check if i == 3
SKIPCOND 400    / Skip next instruction if AC < 0 (i.e., if i == 3)
JUMP ENDLOOP    / Jump to the end of the loop if i == 3
OUTPUT          / Output the value of i
JUMP LOOP       / Jump back to the beginning of the loop
ENDLOOP, HALT   / End of the program

I, DEC 0         / Variable to hold the value of i
THREE, DEC 3     / Constant for comparison
